CMC Markets Posts Loss on Technology Investment, Telegraph Says

-- B y   C a t h e r i n e   A i r l i e
-- 
2011-09-25T06:47:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/cmc-markets-posts-loss-on-technology-investment-telegraph-says.html
CMC Markets Plc, a broker of
financial products, lost 23.7 million pounds ($36.6 million)
before tax after writing off technology investments, the Sunday
Telegraph  reported , citing company founder Peter Cruddas.  Plans for an initial offering of shares in CMC Markets are
believed to be on hold, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Catherine Airlie in London at 
 cairlie@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
